message: The changes that I (Ruby968) have made to the PlusBus website today, 7/12/18 are to give readers more information about our ticketing product and to use our latest PlusBus logo. I am the Commercial Director of Journey Solutions and PlusBus ticketing. Please stop reverting the PlusBus page to older versions.
Undid revision 872487512 by [[Special:Contributions/Davey2010|Davey2010]] ([[User talk:Davey2010|talk]]). Red & White coach OAX9F (image used) was new in 1968 (not 1966). I know as I own the vehicle.
/* Transport */  including information and weblink about Red & White Services Ltd, a bus and coach operator based in Chepstow for 50 years.
Added image used to promote PlusBus ticketing.
Correct date of manufacture of OAX9F image.
Added a bit more detail about what PlusBus tickets are and what they look like. Text drawn from the official PlusBus website at: www.plusbus.info
Installed the new PlusBus logo and more information about the ticket types.
/* Installing a image into our page */ new section
Correct wrong date on photo of OAX9F
The text needed updating and revising. Our logo also needs to be changed, as we have revised it - see our website: www.plusbus.info for details.
